data.description: Welcome to your new home in the desirable Gleneyre neighborhood of Belair. This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers an ideal blend of comfort, convenience, and entertainment, making it a perfect family haven.  As you step into this warm and inviting home, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area and a layout that offers ample natural light throughout. The heart of the home is the large, well-appointed kitchen with plenty of counter space and cabinets, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings.  One of the standout features of this home is the in-ground saltwater heated pool, a private oasis that's ideal for relaxing, hosting summer parties, and creating lasting memories. The fenced backyard ensures both privacy and safety for your loved ones.  Upstairs, the primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and an attached primary bathroom, creating a comfortable and serene retreat. The additional three bedrooms are spacious and perfect for future additions.  The finished basement offers versatility, providing space for a variety of needs from a home gym to a recreation room, and it comes with plenty of storage space.  Stove (2019), Dishwaher (2020), Pool Liner (2019), Pool Pump (2020), HWH (2019), Roof (2011).  Don't miss the opportunity to make this sought-after Gleneyre residence your very own. Contact us today to schedule a showing and discover the potential of this property!
